<i>Previously on</i>
The Last Man on Earth...

00:19.987 --> 00:21.487
MIKE: Looks like
it's just you and me, bud.

00:21.489 --> 00:23.188
I'm the father of her child.
Not anymore.

00:23.190 --> 00:26.692
