(snoring)

00:50.417 --> 00:51.884
(grunts)

00:51.886 --> 00:53.318
Get away from me!

00:53.320 --> 00:54.686
But you... Come on.

00:54.688 --> 00:56.321
Get away from
me, Tandy!

00:56.323 --> 00:58.590
I'm just trying to get you
ready for your big unveiling.

00:58.592 --> 01:00.192
I know what you're
going through right now.
(cow bellows)

01:00.194 --> 01:02.261
You're disoriented,
you're angry...

01:02.263 --> 01:03.429
Damn right, I'm angry!

01:03.431 --> 01:04.763
But you did the right thing

01:04.765 --> 01:07.166
by getting drunk enough to let
me get you into these stocks.

01:07.168 --> 01:08.333
And that's really
gonna score

01:08.335 --> 01:10.002
a bunch of points
with the group, okay?

01:10.004 --> 01:11.403
You ready?
(cow bellows)

01:11.405 --> 01:12.704
Okay, this is
a big moment.
What?

01:12.706 --> 01:14.106
Here we go.
(shouts)
(pot clanging)

01:14.108 --> 01:15.574
Hey, everyone,
come out here!

01:15.576 --> 01:16.708
Get me out of here.

01:16.710 --> 01:17.676
Some really
exciting stuff!

01:17.678 --> 01:19.078
PHIL 2:
Stop it!

01:19.080 --> 01:20.946
TANDY: Phil somehow
put himself in the stocks!

01:20.948 --> 01:22.581
No, I didn't!
It's amazing, right?

01:22.583 --> 01:24.783
What do you mean,
no, you didn't? Yeah, you did.

01:24.785 --> 01:26.952
You're in there right now.
I clearly didn't do it.

01:26.954 --> 01:29.088
What... I'm holding a pot
and something in this hand.

01:29.090 --> 01:30.289
I couldn't have done it.

01:30.291 --> 01:31.790
Wow, we are really
using these things

01:31.792 --> 01:33.459
on a weekly basis now.

01:33.461 --> 01:34.960
If you ask me,
it's too little, too late.

01:34.962 --> 01:36.595
Or do you mean
the exact right amount

01:36.597 --> 01:38.630
at the exact
right time? Hmm?

01:38.632 --> 01:40.365
Erica, Erica,
what do you think, huh?

01:40.367 --> 01:42.568
Pretty cool.
(cow bellowing)

01:42.570 --> 01:45.471
What the goll dang is
up with that cow, huh?

01:45.473 --> 01:47.272
TODD: Oh, my goodness,
guys, get out here!

01:47.274 --> 01:48.440
