01:48.442 --> 01:49.875
No, the show's
in the atrium!

01:49.877 --> 01:51.043
Come on!

01:51.045 --> 01:52.478
Ugh, God.

01:52.480 --> 01:54.079
Okay, I need to go
see what the hell's

01:54.081 --> 01:55.114
going on out there.

01:55.116 --> 01:57.516
Oh, my...
Wow.
Whoa.

02:03.823 --> 02:05.290
(moos)

02:05.292 --> 02:08.460
Holy cow.

02:08.462 --> 02:09.528
Boom.

02:12.932 --> 02:14.166
Hey, little guy or gal.

02:14.168 --> 02:16.401
Not sure what you are,
but you are cute.

02:16.403 --> 02:17.803
Oh, you're a guy. Okay.

02:17.805 --> 02:20.139
Can tell by the...
the penis. Yeah.

02:20.141 --> 02:22.407
Did you guys hear those
noises she was making?

02:22.409 --> 02:24.576
It s-sounded like
she saw the devil.

02:24.578 --> 02:27.579
Yeah, well, she was going
through excruciating pain,

02:27.581 --> 02:29.982
what with the tearing
and the ripping,

02:29.984 --> 02:32.484
and cows don't have doctors
to sew them up.

02:32.486 --> 02:35.621
(clicks tongue)
Oh, I guess we don't either.

02:35.623 --> 02:36.588
Guys, you know what this means?

02:36.590 --> 02:37.856
I mean, there must be
a bull around.

02:37.858 --> 02:40.359
Hey, yeah. Remember when
we first moved in here,

02:40.361 --> 02:42.794
and she'd keep sneaking out
in the middle of the night?

02:42.796 --> 02:44.596
Ah, she was just going off
to do a little

02:44.598 --> 02:47.032
"wham, bam, thank you,
livestock," weren't you?

02:47.034 --> 02:49.268
You little hussy.
TODD: We got to find this bull.

02:49.270 --> 02:51.170
I mean, if we can
get them to mate...

02:51.172 --> 02:52.538
Oh, my God, you are obsessed

02:52.540 --> 02:54.039
with everyone having
more and more babies!

02:54.041 --> 02:56.308
