19:51.824 --> 19:53.324
What do you need?

19:53.326 --> 19:54.959
Well, I said
I was gonna go find the bull,

19:54.961 --> 19:56.294
then come back
and get in the stocks.

19:56.296 --> 19:58.729
So help me get in the stocks.

19:58.731 --> 20:00.865
I thought you were
lying about all that stuff.

20:02.067 --> 20:04.735
I was.

20:04.737 --> 20:06.404
Now help me get in the stocks.

20:06.406 --> 20:08.472
No, no, no, no, no.

20:08.474 --> 20:09.707
Just sit down.

20:09.709 --> 20:11.375
Eat with us.

20:11.377 --> 20:12.777
Are you sure?

20:14.246 --> 20:15.713
TODD:
Yeah.

20:19.351 --> 20:21.285
It looks good.

20:27.059 --> 20:29.060
Mmm.
Mmm.
Mmm.

